		"description": "Complete admin collection with all analytics and chart endpoints\n\n**Authentication Required**: Yes (Admin Role)\n**Header**: Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}\n\n**Rate Limits**:\n- Admin endpoints: 200 requests / minute\n- Chart endpoints: 30 requests / minute\n- User management: 100 requests / minute\n\n**Base URL**: {{baseUrl}}/v1\n\n**NEW Endpoints**:\n- 10 Chart aggregation endpoints for admin dashboard\n- Enhanced analytics endpoints\n- Real-time Socket.IO info",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
